    "rationale": "Despite the Not Accepted COU-level decision on the underlying model submission, the UnitOfAssurance package itself is formally accepted as a complete credibility evidence record for regulatory submission purposes. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated or explicitly flagged as epistemic gaps with justification. The Monte Carlo UQ sweep over boundary conditions is documented. Deficiencies are transparently reported and constitute the basis for required remediation prior to device clearance. Package accepted as evidentiary record; model not accepted for regulatory decision support at this time.",
